현상이 발생한다.</span><br /><br /><span style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Tahoma, gulim; line-height: 16.890625px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">윈도우 압축 파일을 리눅스에서 사용할 경우에도 동일한 현상이 발생한다.</span><br /><br /><span style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Tahoma, gulim; line-height: 16.890625px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">- 한글 파일을 압축 및 여러 수단을 이동 후</span><br /><br /><span style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Tahoma, gulim; line-height: 16.890625px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"># convmv -f cp949 -t utf8 --notest -r .</span><br /><span id=\"callbacknestblogpageskr5891364\" style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Tahoma, gulim; line-height: 16.890625px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); width: 1px; height: 1px; float: right;\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Tahoma, gulim; line-height: 16.890625px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"># convmv -f utf-8 -t euc-kr --notest&nbsp;한글.txt</span><br /><br /><span style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Tahoma, gulim; line-height: 16.890625px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">이미 UTF8 라고 나올때는, --nosmart 옵션을 사용하면 된다. (convmv 1.09 기준)</span><br /><br /><span style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Tahoma, gulim; line-height: 16.890625px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">tar 압축을 사용할 경우 별도 옵션이 없다.</span><br /><br /><span style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Tahoma, gulim; line-height: 16.890625px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">그러나&nbsp;zip 압축을 사용하는 방법이 있다.</span><br /><br /><span style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Tahoma, gulim; line-height: 16.890625px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">zip 에는 문자셋을 지정할 수 있는 옵션이 있다. (단, 압축할때는 불가능하고 압축을 풀때만 가능)</span><br /><br /><span style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Tahoma, gulim; line-height: 16.890625px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"># zip 한글.zip 한글.txt</span><br /><br /><span style=\"color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: Tahoma, gulim; line-height: 16.890625px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"># unzip -O cp949 한글.zip</span></p>\r\n</span>',1,0,0,0,0,0,NULL,'t140','140','shin',140,'shinhee.yi@devmon.co.kr','',NULL,'N;','20131111113201','20131111113201',NULL,'1.222.43.250',-966,-966,'Y','N','PUBLIC','ALLOW'),(967,564,566,'ko','N','jzebra - 웹에서 프린터를 직접 제어하는 RAW 프린팅 API (자바애플릿)','N','N','<p><a href=\"http://qzindustries.com/\">http://qzindustries.com/</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://code.google.com/p/jzebra/\">https://code.google.com/p/jzebra/</a></p>\r\n<p><br /></p>\r\n<p><br /></p>\r\n<p>웹에서 미리보기 화면 이런 것 없이 직접 영수증, 바코드 인쇄를 위한 자바 API 애플릿</p>\r\n<a href=\"http://qzindustries.com/\"><p><a href=\"http://qzindustries.com/\"></a></p>\r\n</a>',1,0,0,0,0,0,NULL,'t140','140','shin',140,'shinhee.yi@devmon.co.kr','',NULL,'N;','20131113200808','20131113200808',NULL,'1.222.43.250',-968,-968,'Y','N','PUBLIC','ALLOW'),(970,961,0,'ko','N','To-do List','N','N','<p>1. 구조 다시 잡기</p>\r\n<p>2. db 말머리 통일하기</p>\r\n<p>3. 학교마다 SSL 적용하는 방법 확인하기</p>\r\n<p>4. BID를 번호로만 가져와야하는 문제 해결하기 bid=6 원래는 bid=banner</p>\r\n<p>5.&nbsp;</p>',1,0,0,0,0,0,NULL,'t140','140','shin',140,'shinhee.yi@devmon.co.kr','',NULL,'N;','20131128120212','20131128120212',NULL,'1.222.43.250',-971,-971,'Y','N','PUBLIC','ALLOW'),(972,106,641,'ko','N','PHP로 html 이미지로 변경하기','N','N','<p><br /></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<div editor_component=\"code_highlighter\" code_type=\"Php\" title=\"html 2 image \" first_line=\"1\" collapse=\"false\" highlight=\"\" nogutter=\"false\" style=\"border:#666 1px dotted;border-left:#2AE 5px solid;padding:5px;background:#FAFAFA url(http://www.devmon.co.kr/xe/modules/editor/components/code_highlighter/code.png) no-repeat top right;\">&lt;?&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$html_head&nbsp;=&nbsp;\"&lt;html&gt;&nbsp;&lt;head&gt;&nbsp;&lt;title&gt;some&nbsp;title&lt;/title&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/head&gt;&nbsp;&lt;body&gt;&nbsp;\";&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$text&nbsp;=&nbsp;\"가나다라마바사\";&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$html_foot&nbsp;=&nbsp;\"&lt;/body&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/html&gt;\";&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$padding&nbsp;=&nbsp;10;&nbsp;//10px&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$fsize&nbsp;=&nbsp;12;&nbsp;//font&nbsp;size&nbsp;12&nbsp;pixels&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$ttf&nbsp;&nbsp;=\"./MALGUN.TTF\";&nbsp;//path&nbsp;to&nbsp;windows&nbsp;ttf&nbsp;font&nbsp;file&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$size&nbsp;=&nbsp;imagettfbbox($fsize,&nbsp;0,&nbsp;$ttf,&nbsp;$text);&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$xsize&nbsp;=&nbsp;abs($size[0])&nbsp;+&nbsp;abs($size[2])+($padding*2);&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$ysize&nbsp;=&nbsp;abs($size[5])&nbsp;+&nbsp;abs($size[1])+($padding*2);&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$image&nbsp;=&nbsp;imagecreate($xsize,&nbsp;$ysize);&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$white&nbsp;=&nbsp;imagecolorallocate&nbsp;($image,&nbsp;255,&nbsp;255,&nbsp;255);&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$black&nbsp;=&nbsp;imagecolorallocate&nbsp;($image,&nbsp;0,&nbsp;0,&nbsp;0);&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;imagefilledrectangle&nbsp;($image,&nbsp;0,&nbsp;0,&nbsp;$xsize,&nbsp;$ysize,&nbsp;$white);&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;imagettftext($image,&nbsp;$fsize,&nbsp;0,&nbsp;$padding,&nbsp;$fsize+$padding,&nbsp;$black,&nbsp;$ttf,&nbsp;$text);&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//save&nbsp;to&nbsp;file&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;imagejpeg($image,\"./screenshot.jpg\",85);&nbsp;//85%quality&nbsp;<br />\r\necho&nbsp;$html_head;&nbsp;<br />\r\necho\"&lt;img&nbsp;src=\'screenshot.jpg\'&gt;\";&nbsp;<br />\r\necho&nbsp;$html_foot;&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;imagedestroy($image);&nbsp;&nbsp;//완료후&nbsp;메모리에서&nbsp;내림<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n?&gt;</div><p></p>\r\n